{"tid":1928420,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[有source呢個先係真]意大利外長迪馬約對中國表示感謝，並斥歐洲盟國沒有表達相同的協助意願","createTime":"2020-03-16T11:23:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-16T13:36:09.000Z","uid":31215,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"1b682b1d525afafa8eb63f7230a925486b96a1e9","tid":1928420,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T11:23:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2590585/%E3%80%90%E6%84%8F%E5%A4%A7%E5%88%A9%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E3%80%91%E6%84%8F%E5%A4%A7%E5%88%A9%E5%A4%96%E9%95%B7%E6%8B%8D%E7%89%87%20%E6%84%9F%E8%AC%9D%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2590585%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%2584%258F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%2588%25A9%25E7%2596%25AB%25E6%2583%2585%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%2584%258F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%2588%25A9%25E5%25A4%2596%25E9%2595%25B7%25E6%258B%258D%25E7%2589%2587%2520%25E6%2584%259F%25E8%25AC%259D%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%258F%2590%25E4%25BE%259B%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9&d=eokTwrWYlXUgHXHl4H%2BebQy1DEY80m5I9K8mtjxpzv8%3D&h=e7108cd0\" target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2590585/%E3%80%90%E6%84%8F%E5%A4%A7%E5%88%A9%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E3%80%91%E6%84%8F%E5%A4%A7%E5%88%A9%E5%A4%96%E9%95%B7%E6%8B%8D%E7%89%87%20%E6%84%9F%E8%AC%9D%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9</a><br />\n<br />\n新型冠狀病毒肺炎疫情在意大利迅速蔓延，中國自身疫情亦十分嚴重，不忘向意大利伸出援手，提供口罩、呼吸機等醫療物資。意大利外長迪馬約（Luigi Di Maio）對中國表示感謝，並斥歐洲盟國沒有表達相同的協助意願。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">迪馬約在Facebook發短片，對中方表達團結的行為表達謝意。意大利疫情嚴峻，醫療用品供應緊張之際，中國紅十字會提供30噸口罩、心肺呼吸機等物資，貨機周四抵達意大利，助解燃眉之急。</span><br />\n<br />\n迪馬約稱，中國並派了醫生及冠狀病毒專家，馳援意大利，強調意大利並不孤單，世上有願意幫助意大利的人。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，德國、法國等歐洲國家，都表明無意出口口罩，迪馬約暗斥歐洲盟國對意大利的幫助，反而有所不及，並指歐洲央行本應出手相助，卻未有這樣做，導致意大利股市暴瀉。<br />\n<br />\n歐洲央行日前公布議息結果，疫情陰霾下未有減息，但有增加資產購買計劃規模，並公布長期再融資操作(LTROs)，向銀行提供額外流動性，以及降低定向長期再融資操作（TLTRO III）的息率。<br />\n<br />\n迪馬約（Luigi Di Maio）facebook:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/LuigiDiMaio/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FLuigiDiMaio%2F&d=eokTwrWYlXUgHXHl4H%2BebQy1DEY80m5I9K8mtjxpzv8%3D&h=09bdc1b1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/LuigiDiMaio/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KCv8mBC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKCv8mBC.jpg&h=71c96aa3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n邊條仆街話意大利外相屌中國???"},{"pid":"2eea716ae21fa35af8d6b29c6174c5000466348f","tid":1928420,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T11:24:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"180173e935e2d69f2932655644ca6e46fdcda0c5","tid":1928420,"uid":308567,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T11:24:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1Zrzha3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1Zrzha3.gif&h=6ff651e4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d46ab4ccef4a138d403c257f50b1c72e8ba39240","tid":1928420,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T11:24:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66a6167bb5ab4ad701cb20fe3219c7474d7f4f2c","tid":1928420,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T11:24:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc04560ad7d3b01945bf1ee081cf2f1f282680d8","tid":1928420,"uid":66087,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T11:25:03.000Z","